			<footer>
				<h3>NOTES</h3>
				<p>This ROI Model has two key areas for cost savings: Reducing IT Infrastructure costs by moving to a PaaS and reducing development time and man-days by leveraging configuation (typically 80%+ with non-programmer time) and code (faster by leveraging prebuilt business logic in the PaaS).</p>
				<p>An opening Mutual Value Discovery calculation should start with testing a planning assumption of paying 576.00 per User per Annum for PaaS Licenses that are Unlimited Edition: Unlimited Apps and amortising PaaS costs into number of Apps. Smaller projects can use 1 App or 10 App pricing above.</p>
